entries.femaleVariant: Was hoping you'd make less trouble getting here.
You're here, finally.
I don't have that kind of authority. Yet.
Didn't wanna trip any alarms. Had to come through quietly.
Fast forward a year…
All right, I'll do what I can.
V, what the hell were you thinking?
What?
I do. Either you leave Clouds or I kill you next.
Matter of fact, I do. Either you walk away and never come back to Clouds...
What might that be?
They'll have their revenge. You've turned Clouds into a ticking time bomb.
Thanks.
Don't want your eddies.
Thanks.
Don't need your eddies.
At midday tomorrow I will present to you terms to which you will agree.
I'll think about it.
Don't mention it. I know what a well-performed service is worth.
But you can have them and have Judy wrapped around your neck.
Your engagement ends here. If ever you should require stable employ, we are not difficult to find.
A little less than I expected for assisting in an internal gang coup.
Skimping from day one, I see.
You blackmailed the leaders of one of Night City's most powerful gangs.
Really think you'da come out the other end alive if I hadn't been there?
entries.maleVariant: You really think you'da come out the other end alive if I hadn't been here?

entries.femaleVariant: Skimping from the get-go… You'll make a fab boss, can tell already.
entries.maleVariant: Skimping from the get-go, heh… You'll make a fab boss, can tell already.

entries.femaleVariant: Touché. Here's a bonus. Let's go celebrate my first day.
Luckily, they're all jacked into virtus, it'd be game over otherwise.
Could've called off the guards, you know. Would've been quicker, simpler.
Who're the other two?
Who're the other two?
"Don't have authority yet?" Sound sure of yourself.
Don't have authority "yet"? Sound damn sure of yourself.
entries.maleVariant: You don't have authority "yet"? Heh, you sound damn sure of yourself.

entries.femaleVariant: Left no room for error. We're exactly where we need to be.
Target audience of today's presentation. Hiromi answers to them directly, now they're gonna watch him die in a pool of his own piss.
One show ends, another begins. Just as good and unforgettable, understand?
I'm about to jack 'em out. They will not be chirpy after the rude awakening.
Do my best. Jack' em out.
This wasn't the plan.
I told you – no killing.
No killing. I said it from the start.
entries.maleVariant: No killing! I said it from the start.

entries.femaleVariant: Let's do this.
You could've called off the guards.
Can we get this over with?
That's our target. Hiromi Sato.
What're they watchin'?
What're they watchin'?
Demo reel of Clouds' next top doll. Specially selected by yours truly.
Oh, please. Mean that wasn't you being noble for your sweet little Judy's benefit?
Don't wanna kill? Don't. All I need is for him to grovel and plead for his life on his polished floor.
Understood?
Maiko, our plan made no allowance for witnesses.
A show of force, we said. And any show requires an audience.
Well, she is no Parker… Wait, what's going on? Who is this?
Lucky girl's gonna replace Evelyn. Hope she proves smarter.
I promised to help Judy, and here we are – thanks to her. But little Jude's cut from a different cloth than you and me.
Can't beat the system – I know it, you know it. And forget about bypassing it.
Correct me if I'm wrong... but in this drama, you were supposed to nod when prompted and use your strength at the right time.
Living proof that Hiromi Sato's time is up.
Clouds declares its independence.
Hiromi has to go.
Dolls at Clouds are declaring their independence. Club'll be run by them and only them.
Hiromi's gotta go.
Tyger Claws'll get a cut of the revenue, but they'll have no say in how the club is run.
Stop this right now!
So I have been told. And what then?
V! Let me do the talking.
Maiko'll run things as she does now. Only officially so.
Clouds will be a doll collective.
Maiko'll make sure you receive a steady flow of funds in exchange for full autonomy. She'll continue running things as she has run them till now…
Clouds doesn't need bosses. Dolls'll take care of the club and themselves.
Maeda-san?
I have nothing to add.
V. I think you're forgetting something. I'll replace Mr. Sato.
I detest chaos and fucking anarchy.
Hiromi will answer for his incompetence. Later.
Will you execute all the clients and leave the dolls to fuck one another instead?
Jack 'em out.
I'll get everything under control.
Have you any idea what's gonna happen now?
Or I end you here and now.
I see you got everything planned out… But you forgot just one thing. I've also got a dollchip.
Can't know that for sure.
That's no longer your problem.
Not your problem anymore. Just let it go and get out.
entries.maleVariant: It's not your problem anymore. Just let it go and get out.

entries.femaleVariant: Can't know that for sure. Maybe the lives we cut short'll be enough for the Claws.
entries.maleVariant: We can't know that for sure. Maybe the lives we cut short'll be enough for the Claws.

entries.femaleVariant: They wiped their hands of the Mox, maybe Clouds is due its freedom now. Time to let it go, Maiko.
entries.maleVariant: They wiped their hands of the Mox, maybe... Clouds is due its freedom now. Time to let it go, Maiko.

entries.femaleVariant: Maybe I will… but not before I paint the walls with your blood.
You tried to cheat us all.
Tried to pull a fast one on everybody, didn't ya? Jumped aboard the liberation train, pretending you wanted to help…
But all you wanted was to take Hiromi's place.
Bravo. But you missed just one detail. I still can. And no one can stop me. Not their corpses, not yours.
They do profit and loss better than Militech's CEO. They'll see it's not worth it.
Get out. Get out now!
She's dreaming if she thinks you can have justice and peace in Night City without cuts, bruises and blood.
Only way's to jump in with both feet, grab power from within.
Do your thing.
Meanin' you wanna replace Hiromi.
Maiko is taking over Clouds.
Maiko'll take care of day-to-day operations at Clouds. She's best for the job.
The dolls trust her, follow her into fire. As you can see.
entries.maleVariant: The dolls trust her, they follow her into fire. As you can see.

entries.femaleVariant: You know what always annoyed me about Hiromi? He had no vision.
He's a man who will not scratch the end of his nose unless you tell him with which hand to do it.
Call off this massacre.
We have one last formality to fulfill.
So now nod and go kick some heads in.
Mm-hm.
Even if that means joining the Tyger Claws?
How the fuck else do you expect me to protect Clouds from other gangs?
Don't like this one bit.
Too late for second thoughts. Tom and Roxie've done their part. Your little doll revolution is underway.
Either we consolidate and win it all or let everything go to waste.
Jack 'em out. We'll see what happens.
You're out to replace Hiromi.
Don't like this at all.
Thanks, V. First transfer from Clouds' new manager coming your way.
Keep 'em, buy yourself somethin' nice.
Fine. I'll give you double, but that's my final offer.
This is not what we agreed.
I know the Claws. To them, power is a question of strength, ruthlessness. This is the only way.
Maiko…
Whereas you will answer for your insolence… now.
I know how this needs to play out, better than anyone. You gotta trust me.
Judy, stop.
Hold on. Think you've gone too far.
Hold on, Maiko. Think you're gettin' carried away.
entries.maleVariant: Hold on, Maiko. I think you're gettin' carried away.

entries.femaleVariant: Judy, I can't focus.
Right, wrong – chicks'll give you shit no matter what you do.
I don't like her, either. Tries too hard.
entries.maleVariant: I don't like her, either. She tries too hard.

entries.femaleVariant: Not all girls have to be nice, Johnny. 'Sides, if she's gotta deal with a gang, she shouldn't be.
Look at me. See this?
I have long looked upon Hiromi Sato's foolish, inept endeavors.
V? What the fuck's she doin'?!
Am I to understand that this future manager stands before me now, speaking with such... zeal?
With your permission.
But this… I think it's obvious he has outlived his usefulness.
Clouds needs new management.
Stop this.
I see not all has been agreed...
Thank you.
This is a look of un-fucking-surprise on my face.
This one's a real charmer, too.
Don't like her, either.
Doesn't have to be nice.
I thought this through – many times.
Why're there three guys? What's she playing at?
And now she's invaded Mr. Sato's private residence.
entries.maleVariant: And now he's invaded Mr. Sato's private residence.

entries.femaleVariant: As if that were not enough, this is where Hiromi's sheer incompetence has led all of us to.
What... ? What the hell?
She murdered Oswald Forrest.
This merc has already disturbed the clientele at Clouds once.
Over my dead body! We were gonna get rid of 'em!
Am I to understand these as your conditions?
What's there to focus on? She's screwin' us!
Come with me, V.
But from now on, it'll be official.
You cannot even control your own mercenary.
Didn't wanna raise any alarms.
Was beginning to think you wouldn't make it.
[Draw weapon] Let's cut to the quick.
[Draw weapon] Let's cut to the quick.
Bored of all this chatter. I'd rather we just cut to the quick.
V. You gotta take 'em down! That's why we're here.
